snippet.title: The Edge of Reality: Teaser | Doctor Who
snippet.description:
Coming in 2021 to consoles and PC, "Doctor Who: The Edge of Reality" reimagines and builds upon last year’s VR experience, "The Edge of Time" - with a new and compelling first-person adventure! Find out more here: https://bbc.in/3iHo9Yt

WATCH MORE: 
The Edge of Time: http://bit.ly/DW-EdgeOfTime
Thirteenth Doctor: http://bit.ly/TheThirteenthDoctor
Tenth Doctor: http://bit.ly/DWTenthDoctor
Subscribe to Doctor Who for more exclusive videos: https://bbc.in/SubscribeToDoctorWho

MORE ABOUT DOCTOR WHO:
Welcome to the Doctor Who Channel! Step inside the TARDIS and embark on an epic journey through time and space. From the Doctor's first adventure in 1963 through countless regenerations, here you will find iconic moments, behind the scenes footage, exclusive content and more! This is the ultimate destination for all things from the Whoniverse.
#DoctorWho

This is a commercial channel from BBC Studios. Service information and feedback:  https://www.bbcstudios.com/contact/contact-us/
